<br>
This is because you never parsed yourself with attack levels low enough to prevent you from landing max damage hits.<br>
<br>
I have/had about 80 megs of parsing. On my rogue, if my attack was below 1300 I NEVER landed a max backstab (out of literally thousands). When I went over 1300, I landed for max frequently - like 1 in 8.<br>
<br>
This does not prove that attack raises your max possible damage, but it did prove that higher attack actually allows you to reach it.<br>
<br>
Same parses with my warrior, but was with different numbers. Attack ranging from 1100 to about 1350. Lay out thousands of swings in a bar graph and it didn't take long to figure out which parse was at 1100 and which was at 1350.<br>
<br>
It was not always a huge difference, but for example, in one case my max hit with 1100 was 326. With 1350 my max was 329. The only difference was my attack score and in both parses I landed for those max's many, many times. In theory my max might be 329 even with only 1100 attack, but apparently my chance to hit that hard with that attack is less then 1 in 25,000.<br>
<br>
It is easy then to say raising your attack score has the effect of raising your maximum damage per hit, since that proved 100% statistically true in a fairly large data set, even if it didn't happen for the reasons I assumed, it still happened.<br>
<br>
Cily <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=121&stop=140>7</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=141&stop=160>8</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=161&stop=180>9</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=181&stop=200>10</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=201&stop=220>11</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=221&stop=240>12</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=241&stop=260>13</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=261&stop=280>14</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=281&stop=300>15</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2962.topic&start=301&stop=320>16</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarr